## 3. هيكل Helm Chart

```text
helm/{chart-name}/
├── Chart.yaml
├── values.yaml
├── values-production.example.yaml
├── values-production.yaml          # gitignored
├── values-ci.yaml
├── .helmignore
├── README.md
└── templates/
    ├── _helpers.tpl
    ├── namespace.yaml
    ├── resourcequota.yaml
    ├── networkpolicy-default-deny.yaml
    ├── networkpolicy-allow-internal.yaml
    ├── networkpolicy-allow-ingress.yaml
    ├── serviceaccount.yaml
    ├── hpa.yaml                    # if scalable
    ├── pdb.yaml                    # if replicas ≥ 2
    └── NOTES.txt
```

### Chart.yaml

```yaml
apiVersion: v2
name: <chart-name>
description: <app description>
type: application
version: 0.1.0
appVersion: "1.0.0"
```

### Values Files

| File | Purpose | Git |
|------|---------|-----|
| `values.yaml` | Defaults, no secrets | ✅ |
| `values-production.example.yaml` | Template with empty placeholders | ✅ |
| `values-production.yaml` | Production secrets | ❌ |
| `values-ci.yaml` | Fake values for `helm lint` / `helm template` | ✅ |

### Install / Upgrade

```bash
helm upgrade --install <release> ./helm/<chart> \
  -n <namespace> \
  --create-namespace \
  -f values.yaml \
  -f values-production.yaml \
  --atomic --wait --timeout 10m
```

