## 4. Mandatory Kubernetes Resources

| Resource | When Required |
|----------|---------------|
| **Deployment** / **StatefulSet** | Always — StatefulSet for DB/cache with PVC |
| **Service** | Always — `ClusterIP` only |
| **Ingress** | External-facing services — `className: nginx` |
| **PVC** | Stateful data — `storageClass: longhorn` |
| **NetworkPolicy** | **Always** — 3 policies (see §7) |
| **ServiceAccount** | Always — dedicated SA, not `default` |
| **Secret** | Credentials — pre-created, `existingSecret` in values |
| **ConfigMap** | Non-sensitive config only |
| **ResourceQuota** | Per app namespace |
| **HPA** | Stateless scalable workloads |
| **PDB** | When `replicas ≥ 2` only (never with replicas=1) |
| **RBAC** | Role/RoleBinding when app needs K8s API access |
| **README.md** + **NOTES.txt** + **values.yaml** | Always |

