## 22. Quick Reference

```yaml
# Platform — MUST
ingressClassName: nginx
clusterIssuer: letsencrypt-prod
storageClass: longhorn
ingress.namespace: kube-system          # for NetworkPolicy allow-ingress

# Namespace — MUST
pod-security.kubernetes.io/audit: restricted
pod-security.kubernetes.io/warn: restricted

# Security — MUST (every container)
runAsNonRoot: true
readOnlyRootFilesystem: true
allowPrivilegeEscalation: false
capabilities.drop: [ALL]

# Every pod — MUST
resources.requests: { cpu, memory }
resources.limits: { cpu, memory }
livenessProbe: required
readinessProbe: required

# Longhorn PVC — SHOULD
recurring-job.longhorn.io/default: enabled
```
